
## ATM Simulation
A simple console-based ATM program written in Java.
### What this program can do
 Show account balance
 Deposit money
 Withdraw money
 Handle basic input validation
 Display a menu for user interaction
The program runs in the console and allows users to choose different
options until they exit.
## Java DSA Practice Programs
This section contains basic Java programs related to problem solving.
### Programs included
Finding the sum of array elements
 Finding the maximum element in an array
 Reversing a string
These programs helped me understand how to work with arrays, strings,
loops, and conditions in Java
## Status
This repository is updated as I continue learning and practicing Java.
